#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_3
msgid ""
"Nestled at the meeting point of the Meuse and Sambre rivers, <strong>Namur "
"is a city that whispers stories of centuries past while buzzing with the "
"energy of modern Wallonia.</strong> Once a medieval stronghold and now the "
"capital of the region, Namur offers a rich tapestry of history, culture, "
"architecture, and natural beauty. And there’s no better way to discover it "
"all than from the comfort of a guided bus tour designed to show you both the "
"highlights and the hidden gems."
msgstr ""
"那慕尔坐落于默兹河与桑布尔河交汇处，<strong>这座曾低语着百年传奇的古城，如今"
"正跃动着瓦隆尼亚的现代活力。</strong>它从中世纪要塞蜕变为大区首府，将历史、文"
"化、建筑与自然风光交织成一幅瑰丽画卷。而想要领略它的全部魅力，最好的方式莫过"
"于搭乘舒适的导览巴士——它将带您穿梭于名胜与秘境之间，开启一场深度探索。"

